WEBVTT

00:25.280 --> 00:27.480
We've been wandering around here
for so many days.

00:27.480 --> 00:28.940
Have you found that Zhang—

00:29.120 --> 00:30.380
what's his name again?

00:30.870 --> 00:32.030
Have you found him?

00:33.110 --> 00:33.960
Southeast,

00:34.640 --> 00:35.640
southwest,

00:37.100 --> 00:37.920
east market,

00:38.640 --> 00:39.570
and west market.

00:39.920 --> 00:42.200
Six central ministries, and 32 blocks.

00:43.030 --> 00:44.590
We are here to find someone,

00:44.920 --> 00:46.730
not to study the map of Tangjing.

00:47.200 --> 00:48.330
Come and take a look.

00:48.360 --> 00:49.490
Where is this place?

00:56.030 --> 00:56.630
This

00:57.470 --> 01:00.070
is the former site
of Qingluan Altar in Tangjing.

01:00.070 --> 01:01.960
It is bordered by the Capital Prefecture
to the left

01:01.960 --> 01:03.840
and the Empress's Furong Garden
to the right.

01:03.840 --> 01:05.310
Nominally it has been abandoned
for a long time

01:05.310 --> 01:07.190
and isn't even drawn on the map.

01:07.790 --> 01:10.230
However, it is surrounded
by three watchtowers,

01:10.230 --> 01:12.789
which are guarded day and night.

01:15.870 --> 01:18.100
This is the secret residence of Director Zhang
that we are looking for.

01:18.100 --> 01:19.230
We will act tonight.

02:41.450 --> 02:46.380
[REBIRTH]

02:46.910 --> 02:49.350
[Episode 12]

02:50.960 --> 02:52.370
[Virtue of Zhang's Mansion]

03:28.079 --> 03:29.430
I've searched the east wings.

03:29.430 --> 03:30.350
No one was there.

03:30.350 --> 03:31.680
He's not here. Let's go.

03:46.860 --> 03:48.030
There are traps everywhere.

03:48.030 --> 03:48.660
Let's go.

03:52.270 --> 03:53.150
You're injured?

03:53.150 --> 03:53.910
Who's there?

03:55.730 --> 03:57.190
Go! I'll go lead them away!

04:03.690 --> 04:04.430
The intruders are over there!

04:04.430 --> 04:05.080
After them!

04:05.080 --> 04:05.560
Yes!

04:10.300 --> 04:11.560
The intruders are just ahead!

04:11.560 --> 04:12.280
After them!

04:27.380 --> 04:27.990
Search!

04:45.920 --> 04:46.650
Who's there?

04:52.120 --> 04:53.650
Greetings, Your Highness.

04:53.870 --> 04:55.530
The people you're looking for

04:55.950 --> 04:56.870
went that way.

04:57.110 --> 04:57.670
Yes.

04:57.850 --> 04:58.510
Let's go!

05:05.360 --> 05:06.000
Xing?

05:17.310 --> 05:17.950
Xing,

05:18.710 --> 05:20.440
I know you have many questions,

05:20.920 --> 05:23.070
and I should give you some explanation.

05:23.070 --> 05:24.600
But I have my reasons not to.

05:25.560 --> 05:26.360
Zhuge Yue,

05:27.510 --> 05:29.910
I know you've been protecting me silently.

05:30.310 --> 05:31.480
If it weren't for me,

05:32.040 --> 05:34.770
you wouldn't have nearly died
in the frozen lake.

05:35.600 --> 05:37.680
Xing, it was not your fault.

05:37.870 --> 05:38.800
I...

05:40.270 --> 05:42.400
I thought we had a tacit understanding

05:42.600 --> 05:44.000
and knew each other well.

05:44.480 --> 05:46.600
We even went through
life and death together.

05:46.600 --> 05:47.720
What exactly is it

05:47.720 --> 05:49.680
that we can't face together?

05:52.820 --> 05:55.430
I didn't expect you to still refuse
to tell me.

05:56.750 --> 05:58.360
I could only help you this much today.

05:58.360 --> 05:59.360
From now on,

06:00.160 --> 06:01.240
I will tell myself

06:01.630 --> 06:03.510
that the old Zhuge Yue sank into

06:04.510 --> 06:07.170
the frozen lake forever
while trying to save me.

06:14.940 --> 06:16.010
I'm sorry, Xing.

06:17.060 --> 06:19.460
If I could still stand before you
properly,

06:20.040 --> 06:22.300
I would definitely tell you everything.

06:45.000 --> 06:48.430
The audience has arrived.
Let the show begin!

06:49.170 --> 06:51.170
Today we will present you

06:51.390 --> 06:54.870
"General Chu's Three Attacks
on Zhuge Yue".

06:55.540 --> 06:57.300
The plot has ups and downs

06:57.680 --> 06:59.140
and is deeply satisfying!

06:59.240 --> 07:01.390
It's truly an excellent script.

07:01.710 --> 07:02.270
Li Ce,

07:02.720 --> 07:03.800
you're so lame.

07:05.600 --> 07:06.510
Whether it's lame or not,

07:06.510 --> 07:08.770
you have to watch it before you can judge.

07:09.800 --> 07:10.800
The first strike

07:11.480 --> 07:13.750
is for his eternally cold face.

07:14.190 --> 07:15.040
He has a mouth,

07:15.190 --> 07:16.360
but he never uses it properly.

07:16.360 --> 07:17.830
Keeping a straight face all day,

07:17.830 --> 07:19.720
as if the whole world owes him.

07:24.950 --> 07:25.480
Qiao,

07:25.870 --> 07:27.800
do you think that was a good strike?

07:29.510 --> 07:30.310
Wait a minute.

07:30.600 --> 07:32.000
There's a second strike.

07:32.360 --> 07:33.420
This second strike

07:33.480 --> 07:35.270
is for his arrogance

07:35.270 --> 07:36.270
and superiority.

07:36.390 --> 07:38.830
He's just an ordinary person
made of flesh and blood,

07:38.830 --> 07:40.870
but he has to act like an immortal
descended to earth,

07:40.870 --> 07:42.630
capable of handling all problems.

07:42.630 --> 07:43.490
And the result?

07:48.430 --> 07:50.240
He ended up covered in scars,

07:50.390 --> 07:52.320
which made others feel bad for him.

08:00.750 --> 08:01.960
The third strike

08:03.120 --> 08:05.510
is for Zhuge Yue's self-righteousness.

08:06.270 --> 08:07.750
He always claims

08:07.800 --> 08:09.080
that everything he does

08:09.080 --> 08:10.710
is to protect Qiao.

08:11.390 --> 08:12.570
Without consulting anyone,

08:12.570 --> 08:13.780
he has done many dangerous things

08:13.780 --> 08:15.240
in the name of protection.

08:15.680 --> 08:17.370
Does Qiao need your protection?

08:17.370 --> 08:20.250
Qiao is the world-renowned General Chu.

08:20.720 --> 08:22.830
She can protect herself.

08:33.720 --> 08:34.650
How was it, Qiao?

08:35.360 --> 08:36.490
Do you like the play?

08:36.799 --> 08:37.830
If you do,

08:37.870 --> 08:39.130
I've prepared Act Two.

08:40.240 --> 08:43.320
"General Chu Meets
the Crown Prince of Biantang By Chance,

08:43.320 --> 08:46.140
Fake Drama Turns Into Real Fate."

08:50.270 --> 08:50.960
Li Ce.

08:51.750 --> 08:52.950
I want to have a drink.

08:53.150 --> 08:53.840
Drink?

08:55.270 --> 08:55.950
Li Ce.

08:56.910 --> 08:57.790
Let me ask you.

08:59.000 --> 09:01.800
You said you liked Princess Fu
when you were young.

09:02.670 --> 09:04.240
But besides Princess Fu,

09:05.030 --> 09:07.670
you have so many female confidants
around you,

09:07.910 --> 09:10.600
and a large group
of beauties in your mansion.

09:11.120 --> 09:12.080
Are you sincere

09:13.750 --> 09:15.700
to all of them?

09:17.630 --> 09:18.910
Of course not.

09:20.390 --> 09:21.320
With some,

09:22.200 --> 09:24.320
I'm just playing along.

09:25.360 --> 09:26.270
With others,

09:27.200 --> 09:28.720
they are fair ladies.

09:29.150 --> 09:30.320
As a gentleman,

09:31.270 --> 09:32.550
I must woo them

09:33.550 --> 09:35.280
and take my time to admire them.

09:35.960 --> 09:37.200
It's like...

09:37.630 --> 09:40.200
appreciating a painting
or a piece of music.

09:41.150 --> 09:43.390
As for those I truly like,

09:50.120 --> 09:51.750
there are very, very few.

10:15.460 --> 10:16.770
I don't know why,

10:18.670 --> 10:20.290
but my feelings for him...

10:20.470 --> 10:22.610
are causing me pain.

10:23.750 --> 10:24.840
True love is to feel

10:26.960 --> 10:28.560
what the other person feels.

10:30.360 --> 10:32.030
You can sense his happiness,

10:32.520 --> 10:33.860
so naturally, you can also feel

10:33.860 --> 10:35.820
the pain and struggle in his heart.

10:36.440 --> 10:38.300
You would find joy because of him,

10:39.510 --> 10:42.570
and naturally,
you would also feel pain because of him.

10:48.840 --> 10:49.440
Li Ce,

10:51.390 --> 10:53.440
have you ever truly loved someone?

11:03.550 --> 11:04.950
It has already happened.

11:12.910 --> 11:13.510
Qiao.

11:40.010 --> 11:40.680
Li Ce!

11:45.150 --> 11:45.790
Qiao!

11:51.670 --> 11:52.840
Qiao!

12:54.290 --> 12:55.030
Here you go.

13:08.010 --> 13:08.650
Miss.

13:10.490 --> 13:11.550
What would you like to buy, miss?

13:11.550 --> 13:12.670
What did the lady

13:12.750 --> 13:14.440
just buy from you?

13:14.840 --> 13:16.320
She wasn't here to buy anything.

13:16.320 --> 13:18.720
She left that handkerchief here for sale.

13:18.870 --> 13:20.330
She is a regular customer.

13:20.510 --> 13:21.320
Selling a handkerchief?

13:21.320 --> 13:21.930
Yes.

13:22.240 --> 13:24.680
That lady embroiders a handkerchief
every month

13:24.680 --> 13:26.140
and brings it here to sell.

13:26.210 --> 13:26.750
And every time,

13:26.750 --> 13:28.240
it's sold

13:28.240 --> 13:29.320
within 1 hour.

13:29.510 --> 13:32.270
Do you know the person
who buys her handkerchiefs?

13:32.270 --> 13:33.800
Of course I don't know them.

13:34.200 --> 13:37.030
But it seems to always be the same lady,

13:37.200 --> 13:38.830
wearing a veil and a bamboo hat,

13:38.830 --> 13:40.120
wrapped up so tightly

13:40.400 --> 13:42.400
that her face can't be seen clearly.

13:43.880 --> 13:45.280
Is the handkerchief still here?

13:45.280 --> 13:46.040
Yes.

13:49.300 --> 13:50.960
I'll take this handkerchief.

13:51.320 --> 13:52.080
Here you go.

14:18.100 --> 14:19.300
Where is Wang Shi'er?

14:19.480 --> 14:20.910
He's slacking off
and not practicing again, right?

14:20.910 --> 14:22.150
Do you even need to ask?

14:22.150 --> 14:24.080
He's definitely upstairs, tinkering with

14:24.080 --> 14:25.880
his stupid contraptions again.

14:38.390 --> 14:39.150
Wang Shi'er!

14:45.370 --> 14:46.410
Wang Shi'er!

14:55.890 --> 14:58.130
Beautiful, you are so ruthless.

14:58.750 --> 14:59.960
I like it.

15:07.510 --> 15:08.200
Your Highness!

15:08.200 --> 15:09.360
Your Highness!

15:10.440 --> 15:12.680
Look at these new mechanisms I've set up.

15:12.680 --> 15:14.080
Aren't they pretty good?

15:14.880 --> 15:16.210
I was wrong! I was wrong!

15:16.560 --> 15:17.960
Take a look at this first.

15:21.910 --> 15:24.840
I feel there's something weird
about this handkerchief.

15:24.840 --> 15:25.790
The stitching is uneven,

15:25.790 --> 15:27.840
but it seems to follow a certain pattern.

15:27.840 --> 15:29.100
I can't be sure either.

15:30.360 --> 15:31.240
But I've seen something like this before

15:31.240 --> 15:33.360
in an ancient tomb in the southern border.

15:33.360 --> 15:34.510
Some tombs have symbols

15:34.510 --> 15:37.240
of varying lengths inscribed
to record secret messages.

15:37.240 --> 15:38.570
So you mean these stitches

15:38.570 --> 15:40.940
could be some sort of code?

15:45.420 --> 15:48.000
[Lyvwan Restaurant]

15:56.070 --> 15:58.310
Crown Prince, you're here.

15:59.870 --> 16:01.200
Lord Zhuge Ximeng,

16:01.910 --> 16:03.240
what do you want from me?

16:04.480 --> 16:05.390
I asked you here

16:06.110 --> 16:07.910
to discuss a collaboration with you.

16:07.910 --> 16:08.910
A collaboration?

16:09.000 --> 16:10.600
What kind of collaboration?

16:20.750 --> 16:22.080
I came to Biantang this time

16:22.080 --> 16:23.080
to find someone—

16:23.550 --> 16:25.240
Director Zhang Qingzhao
of the Ministry of Works.

16:25.240 --> 16:26.370
You help me find him,

16:26.630 --> 16:27.600
and I'll pay you.

16:27.670 --> 16:30.070
Director Zhang is a key confidential official
in the Ministry of Works.

16:30.070 --> 16:31.270
Why are you looking for him?

16:31.270 --> 16:33.840
I need a craft diagram he has.

16:34.270 --> 16:35.270
The techniques inside

16:35.270 --> 16:37.120
can help Ximeng mine black gold.

16:37.480 --> 16:38.960
If you're willing to cooperate with me,

16:38.960 --> 16:40.220
after the deal is done,

16:40.240 --> 16:42.360
you'll get 10 percent of the black gold

16:42.360 --> 16:43.200
from this mine.

16:43.200 --> 16:44.800
Ximeng has a black gold mine?

16:46.920 --> 16:49.590
But Director Zhang
is a pillar of Biantang.

16:50.130 --> 16:51.530
For nearly 40 years,

16:51.630 --> 16:53.820
he's been responsible
for all major casting

16:53.820 --> 16:55.560
and metallurgy tasks
in Biantang, including

16:55.560 --> 16:56.670
even military fortifications.

16:56.670 --> 16:58.390
What could
a mere title-holding Crown Prince like me

16:58.390 --> 16:59.360
possibly do to help you?

16:59.360 --> 17:00.390
You're right.

17:00.510 --> 17:02.440
You really can't help me with much.

17:02.720 --> 17:03.910
What do you mean by that?

17:03.910 --> 17:05.030
But first,

17:05.349 --> 17:06.510
currently, as the Crown Prince,

17:06.510 --> 17:07.920
you're responsible for my travels.

17:07.920 --> 17:09.270
You're like a sticky plaster

17:09.270 --> 17:10.400
I can't shake off.

17:10.690 --> 17:12.730
So it's better to be frank with you.

17:13.339 --> 17:14.869
I'm warning you, Zhuge Yue,

17:14.880 --> 17:16.349
if you keep talking like this,
we're done here.

17:16.349 --> 17:17.160
Second,

17:17.240 --> 17:19.000
although you have no power or influence,

17:19.000 --> 17:20.740
that's actually your strength.

17:20.740 --> 17:21.500
Strength?

17:21.880 --> 17:23.400
You are a puppet Crown Prince,

17:23.400 --> 17:25.109
so you need

17:25.109 --> 17:26.829
this 10 percent
of black gold more than anyone else.

17:26.829 --> 17:28.690
Are you saying I'm short of money?

17:28.920 --> 17:29.790
Who are you looking down on?

17:29.790 --> 17:31.850
You are the Crown Prince of Biantang.

17:32.070 --> 17:33.200
Without this 10 percent of the black gold,

17:33.200 --> 17:34.960
you naturally
won't lack food and clothing.

17:34.960 --> 17:36.220
But what if you have it?

17:37.070 --> 17:39.110
Perhaps you could turn the tables.

17:39.480 --> 17:40.350
You never know.

17:43.640 --> 17:45.310
But why should I cooperate with you?

17:45.310 --> 17:46.240
You are neither from Biantang,

17:46.240 --> 17:47.200
nor from Ximeng.

17:47.330 --> 17:48.730
Why should I believe you?

17:50.830 --> 17:53.070
But who else can you trust except me?

17:53.200 --> 17:54.720
Since you said
you only hold an empty title,

17:54.720 --> 17:55.880
I believe that in Biantang,

17:55.880 --> 17:57.830
you don't have many people you can trust.

17:57.830 --> 17:58.590
In that case,

17:58.590 --> 18:01.200
what does it matter whose side I'm on?

18:06.310 --> 18:07.000
Zhuge Yue,

18:07.330 --> 18:08.400
do you have a knife in your mouth?

18:08.400 --> 18:09.960
Why are you speaking so harshly?

18:09.960 --> 18:10.550
I just confessed my feelings

18:10.550 --> 18:12.450
to Qiao last night and got rejected.

18:12.450 --> 18:14.030
Now I'm pissed off because of you.

18:14.030 --> 18:15.630
What terrible luck do I have?

18:21.720 --> 18:22.510
Really?

18:23.310 --> 18:24.710
I didn't know about this.

18:25.110 --> 18:26.070
Sorry for what I said

18:26.070 --> 18:27.160
that upset you.

18:27.650 --> 18:28.890
I am truly sorry.

18:29.100 --> 18:29.960
How about this?

18:30.720 --> 18:31.780
As an apology,

18:33.070 --> 18:35.110
after this is done, I'll ask King Ximeng

18:35.110 --> 18:37.070
to give you an extra 10 percent
as compensation.

18:37.070 --> 18:38.070
What do you think?

18:40.720 --> 18:41.510
Zhuge Yue,

18:42.240 --> 18:42.960
come on!

18:42.960 --> 18:44.160
Please hide the smile on your face

18:44.160 --> 18:45.720
before you apologize to me, okay?

18:45.720 --> 18:46.440
Are you that happy

18:46.440 --> 18:47.970
that I was rejected by Qiao?

19:17.690 --> 19:25.100
[Chunxiao Theater]

19:56.360 --> 19:56.990
Take care.

20:01.180 --> 20:02.040
Your Highness,

20:02.400 --> 20:03.330
please come out.

20:09.590 --> 20:11.200
When did you notice me?

20:11.830 --> 20:12.920
During the day at the market,

20:12.920 --> 20:14.880
I saw you buy my handkerchief.

20:15.240 --> 20:16.590
On my way here just now,

20:17.000 --> 20:18.890
I sensed someone following me,

20:19.680 --> 20:21.000
so I guessed it was you.

20:21.240 --> 20:24.070
So you admit that the handkerchief

20:24.590 --> 20:26.510
is a tool for you
and the women in this theater

20:26.510 --> 20:27.790
to pass messages?

20:28.110 --> 20:28.680
Yes.

20:30.240 --> 20:32.040
It's hard for us to meet usually,

20:32.350 --> 20:35.010
so we've been using this method
to communicate.

20:39.720 --> 20:41.000
Who are you?

20:41.000 --> 20:42.590
You have already seen Rou.

20:42.830 --> 20:44.630
I can't hide it from you anymore.

20:45.510 --> 20:47.550
I was once a noble lady in Biantang.

20:48.000 --> 20:49.000
Twenty years ago,

20:49.680 --> 20:52.440
my father was involved
in the succession struggle

20:52.440 --> 20:54.270
between the current emperor
and his eldest brother,

20:54.270 --> 20:55.600
Crown Prince Maocheng.

20:56.590 --> 20:57.810
He was eventually implicated,

20:57.810 --> 21:00.170
and all my family members were executed.

21:01.790 --> 21:03.270
I was sold as a slave.

21:04.510 --> 21:06.480
Rou went through the same thing as I did.

21:06.480 --> 21:08.440
She also became a slave because of

21:08.640 --> 21:10.370
the palace coup at Xuri Palace.

21:10.800 --> 21:12.750
That's when we met.

21:16.510 --> 21:17.480
At first,

21:19.000 --> 21:19.880
Rou and I

21:19.880 --> 21:21.680
were sold to a brothel as slaves.

21:22.070 --> 21:24.000
We only did the lowest kind of work,

21:24.510 --> 21:25.930
didn't have enough to eat,

21:25.930 --> 21:28.510
and we weren't even allowed
to serve customers.

21:28.510 --> 21:30.440
In order to keep us alive,

21:31.330 --> 21:32.250
I stole

21:33.000 --> 21:34.370
and was beaten.

21:35.510 --> 21:36.240
Later,

21:37.000 --> 21:38.730
a customer took a liking to Rou,

21:39.480 --> 21:42.010
which is how
she entered a theater to perform.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.110
And I

21:47.880 --> 21:48.700
did everything I could,

21:48.700 --> 21:51.560
became a high-ranking servant
who could serve tea,

21:51.880 --> 21:55.000
and was eventually bought and sent
into the Crown Prince's Mansion,

21:55.000 --> 21:56.720
where I gained the Crown Prince's favor.

21:56.720 --> 21:59.720
Over the years,
I've been using my looks to please men,

22:00.920 --> 22:02.110
just to earn enough

22:02.110 --> 22:04.110
to keep Rou and me alive.

22:04.800 --> 22:06.350
The handkerchief you bought

22:06.350 --> 22:08.660
is how Rou and I secretly communicate.

22:09.510 --> 22:12.200
The code hidden in the stitches
is a form of women's script

22:12.200 --> 22:13.440
that Rou and I use

22:13.440 --> 22:15.500
to convey our feelings to each other.

22:16.750 --> 22:18.410
And the package I just gave her

22:20.440 --> 22:21.160
contained jewelry I secretly took

22:21.160 --> 22:23.200
from the Crown Prince's Mansion

22:23.730 --> 22:24.900
to support her.

22:25.000 --> 22:26.160
Does Li Ce know

22:27.240 --> 22:28.510
all of this?

22:28.510 --> 22:31.310
Your Highness,
I have no intention of harming him.

22:31.400 --> 22:32.890
His Highness is a good man.

22:32.910 --> 22:35.110
I will do my best to serve him.

22:35.640 --> 22:36.720
But if our backgrounds

22:36.720 --> 22:37.920
are ever discovered,

22:41.030 --> 22:44.360
I'm afraid even His Highness
wouldn't be able to protect us.

22:55.720 --> 22:57.780
You've been following me all the way.

23:06.270 --> 23:08.920
Why did you go and see
the Crown Prince of Biantang?

23:08.920 --> 23:09.670
I need him.

23:09.700 --> 23:11.560
What can someone like him even do?

23:12.390 --> 23:14.070
I've looked into Director Zhang.

23:14.070 --> 23:15.310
He is extremely cautious

23:15.310 --> 23:17.650
and has more than one residence
here in Tangjing,

23:17.650 --> 23:19.120
and his whereabouts are highly secret.

23:19.120 --> 23:21.450
He is not greedy for money, women,
or fame.

23:21.480 --> 23:22.790
He either stays indoors all day

23:22.790 --> 23:24.450
or is always heavily guarded.

23:24.590 --> 23:25.640
To find him,

23:25.830 --> 23:27.440
I need someone in Biantang

23:27.440 --> 23:28.750
who can move around freely.

23:28.750 --> 23:29.830
So you told him

23:29.830 --> 23:30.830
everything?

23:33.840 --> 23:35.300
How dare you ruin our plan?

23:41.830 --> 23:43.510
Don't resort to violence so easily.

23:43.510 --> 23:44.160
Also,

23:44.620 --> 23:45.900
don't follow me again.

23:51.370 --> 23:54.380
[Fuhe Pavilion]

24:06.310 --> 24:06.920
Qiao,

24:07.020 --> 24:07.930
you came just in time.

24:07.930 --> 24:09.140
I encountered something yesterday.

24:09.140 --> 24:10.350
-I want to discuss it with you.
-Li Ce.

24:10.350 --> 24:12.070
I also have something to discuss with you.

24:12.070 --> 24:13.590
It's about Lady Ziming.

24:13.830 --> 24:14.550
Ziming?

24:14.810 --> 24:15.720
What happened to her?

24:15.720 --> 24:17.380
Lady Ziming has a close friend

24:17.480 --> 24:18.200
named Rou.

24:18.880 --> 24:19.810
Do you know that?

24:23.690 --> 24:24.940
Here, enjoy.

24:25.200 --> 24:26.400
If it's the head, I'll send her away;

24:26.400 --> 24:27.840
if it's the tail, I won't.

24:31.660 --> 24:33.590
That doesn't count. One more time.

24:34.790 --> 24:37.720
You said yesterday
you would go back and think about it.

24:37.720 --> 24:38.780
How's the thinking going?

24:38.780 --> 24:39.640
Thinking what?

24:43.480 --> 24:44.160
I forgot.

24:44.640 --> 24:46.550
I had a more important thing
to think about yesterday,

24:46.550 --> 24:47.880
so I had no time for that.

24:48.950 --> 24:49.690
What was it?

24:49.720 --> 24:50.700
Since it's important,

24:50.700 --> 24:53.230
I naturally can't tell just anyone
so easily.

24:59.720 --> 25:01.350
Well, Zhuge Yue.

25:02.050 --> 25:04.180
we've known each other for a while now.

25:04.240 --> 25:06.000
We can be considered good brothers.

25:06.000 --> 25:07.400
Let me ask you something.

25:07.480 --> 25:09.080
You must answer truthfully.

25:09.190 --> 25:11.120
What do you think of me?

25:16.680 --> 25:17.310
Wait.

25:18.350 --> 25:21.350
I'm handsome, suave,

25:21.500 --> 25:23.240
elegant, and talented—

25:23.240 --> 25:25.700
there's no need
to mention those qualities.

25:27.550 --> 25:28.720
I mean,

25:28.720 --> 25:29.750
do I have any

25:29.750 --> 25:30.920
imperfections?

25:31.470 --> 25:32.330
For example...

25:32.350 --> 25:33.460
You talk too much.

25:34.310 --> 25:35.400
I talk too much?

25:35.880 --> 25:36.630
Then I'll stop talking.

25:36.630 --> 25:37.220
Wait!

25:39.960 --> 25:41.690
Why are we eating wontons here?

25:52.530 --> 25:53.250
Here you go.

26:03.080 --> 26:04.040
See that man?

26:05.270 --> 26:07.400
He should be Director Zhang's butler.

26:08.960 --> 26:11.640
Director Zhang
has more than one hidden residence.

26:11.640 --> 26:13.880
A few days ago, I sneaked into one of
his secret residences in the north of the city.

26:13.880 --> 26:14.880
I didn't find him,

26:15.110 --> 26:16.400
but I found some clues

26:16.720 --> 26:18.960
linked to this wonton stall.

26:20.480 --> 26:21.720
If I'm not mistaken,

26:22.200 --> 26:24.800
his second secret residence
should be nearby.

26:24.850 --> 26:27.570
The wontons
were bought for him by his butler.

26:37.610 --> 26:39.410
You came to see me for something?

26:47.720 --> 26:48.440
What is it?

26:52.070 --> 26:52.790
This matter

26:53.520 --> 26:54.680
is quite serious.

26:55.110 --> 26:56.310
Then say it quickly.

26:56.450 --> 26:57.140
It's...

26:58.510 --> 26:59.960
hard to explain in a few words.

26:59.960 --> 27:01.910
Then tell me once you've figured out
how to explain it.

27:01.910 --> 27:03.060
Qiao, don't go.

27:03.080 --> 27:04.810
Don't be so impatient. Come on.

27:05.030 --> 27:05.830
I'll tell you.

27:08.100 --> 27:09.210
In short,

27:09.240 --> 27:11.300
Ximeng has a lot of gold underground,

27:11.320 --> 27:13.150
but they can't mine it, so they're getting
anxious but can't do anything about it.

27:13.150 --> 27:14.790
Zhuge Yue came to me
to propose a cooperation.

27:14.790 --> 27:16.720
He asked me to help him find Director Zhang
from the Ministry of Works

27:16.720 --> 27:17.880
and his manufacturing diagram,

27:17.880 --> 27:19.310
and he promised me

27:19.590 --> 27:21.240
one-tenth of the profits afterward.

27:21.240 --> 27:21.790
No,

27:22.590 --> 27:23.550
two-tenths.

27:23.790 --> 27:25.240
What are you talking about?

27:25.240 --> 27:26.700
Princess, Your Highness.

27:26.790 --> 27:28.450
Ziming requests an audience.

27:33.710 --> 27:35.030
I'm sorry, Your Highness.

27:35.030 --> 27:36.560
Dear, what are you doing?

27:37.000 --> 27:38.720
I've been concealing something
from you, Your Highness,

27:38.720 --> 27:40.180
and I feel guilty about it.

27:41.330 --> 27:43.520
Although I have failed your favor,

27:43.640 --> 27:44.740
I beg you, Your Highness,

27:44.740 --> 27:46.240
for the sake of the child in my womb,

27:46.240 --> 27:47.310
do not send me away.

27:48.880 --> 27:51.110
I am pregnant with your child.

27:51.330 --> 27:52.140
Child?

28:03.030 --> 28:04.890
Congratulations, Elder Helian.

28:05.070 --> 28:06.510
The day before yesterday, His Majesty

28:06.510 --> 28:08.540
announced the news
of making Lady Helian his concubine

28:08.540 --> 28:09.490
to the world.

28:10.680 --> 28:12.440
This has finally put us tribe elders

28:12.440 --> 28:13.510
of Great Yan

28:14.160 --> 28:15.240
at ease.

28:15.480 --> 28:17.830
The future of Great Yan is now secured.

28:20.750 --> 28:23.310
I always thought His Majesty
was reluctant to take a queen

28:23.310 --> 28:25.840
because he still had feelings
for that slave.

28:26.050 --> 28:28.690
Even the niece I sent to him

28:28.710 --> 28:30.640
was sent back without hesitation.

28:31.240 --> 28:33.440
I didn't expect that Helian Tribe,

28:34.350 --> 28:36.280
though poor at riding and warfare,

28:37.350 --> 28:38.480
to be so clever

28:39.830 --> 28:41.880
when it comes to offering women.

28:44.110 --> 28:47.070
Elder Pale, you must be joking.

28:49.640 --> 28:50.240
Enough of this.

28:50.240 --> 28:51.830
Come, come, let's drink.

28:52.310 --> 28:53.070
Come on.

28:54.090 --> 28:55.570
Come on, let's drink.

28:57.960 --> 28:58.750
Good wine.

28:59.240 --> 28:59.880
Elders,

28:59.880 --> 29:02.410
since you are here to congratulate me
on becoming the Queen,

29:02.410 --> 29:04.960
why did you start the banquet
without me?

29:05.590 --> 29:06.550
Why are you here?

29:06.760 --> 29:07.890
If I hadn't come,

29:08.080 --> 29:10.110
how would I know
who are the Helian Tribe's friends

29:10.110 --> 29:11.750
and who are our enemies?

29:12.510 --> 29:14.320
And how could I speak well of you

29:14.350 --> 29:16.020
before His Majesty?

29:18.280 --> 29:21.440
The Helian Tribe
has truly become something.

29:22.480 --> 29:25.440
We'll have to be more careful
with our words in the future.

29:25.440 --> 29:28.590
Although the Helian Tribe has no troops,

29:29.640 --> 29:31.320
it has women.

29:33.920 --> 29:35.380
Elder Pale, you're right.

29:36.160 --> 29:38.070
I used to think

29:38.070 --> 29:40.200
only troops could strengthen a tribe.

29:40.680 --> 29:42.790
But now I finally realize

29:43.680 --> 29:44.680
that sometimes,

29:45.310 --> 29:47.960
women can be very different
from each other.

29:48.640 --> 29:50.440
If a woman is a princess consort,

29:50.750 --> 29:53.280
she can be more valuable
than thousands of men

29:53.280 --> 29:55.890
and thousands of fine cavalry.

29:55.920 --> 29:56.480
You...

29:57.880 --> 29:59.830
Princess Consort Helian,
you're absolutely right.

29:59.830 --> 30:01.310
Although His Majesty
is wise and formidable,

30:01.310 --> 30:02.640
he is also inscrutable.

30:02.920 --> 30:03.960
We have long been troubled by the fact

30:03.960 --> 30:05.960
that he has no one truly close to him.

30:06.030 --> 30:07.160
Now that we have you,

30:07.440 --> 30:10.570
we hope you will look after us,
Princess Consort Helian.

30:13.480 --> 30:14.410
You're too kind.

30:15.790 --> 30:17.830
Although His Majesty favors me now,

30:17.830 --> 30:20.030
the Helian Tribe is still weak.

30:20.400 --> 30:22.720
I will still need your support.

30:23.510 --> 30:24.550
You flatter us.

30:24.830 --> 30:26.440
You've just been named Princess Consort.

30:26.440 --> 30:28.270
You must have a lot of things
to deal with.

30:28.270 --> 30:29.730
We will take our leave now.

30:29.920 --> 30:30.510
Let's go.

30:30.750 --> 30:31.560
Farewell.

30:32.570 --> 30:33.160
Let's go.

30:34.810 --> 30:35.400
Let's go!

30:46.880 --> 30:48.740
I am the chief of the Helian Tribe.

30:49.230 --> 30:51.960
Who allowed you to come here
and tell me what to do?

30:58.590 --> 30:59.480
Helian Chuan,

31:00.240 --> 31:01.330
listen carefully.

31:02.480 --> 31:05.790
From now on, you are
the head of the family in name only.

31:06.400 --> 31:07.440
In reality,

31:08.350 --> 31:10.480
I am the Princess Consort of Great Yan.

31:10.750 --> 31:12.160
You must always remember

31:13.110 --> 31:14.070
that without me,

31:16.680 --> 31:17.680
you are nothing but a coward

31:17.680 --> 31:19.550
who sold your sister's body

31:19.550 --> 31:22.960
for a few worthless horses.

31:28.450 --> 31:29.050
Do it!

31:29.960 --> 31:31.000
Kill me!

31:31.230 --> 31:33.400
Then send my body to Yan Xun.

31:40.160 --> 31:41.160
You loser.

32:01.370 --> 32:02.880
Yesterday,
I wrote a letter to Director Zhang

32:02.880 --> 32:04.270
in your name.

32:06.960 --> 32:08.440
I bribed the stall owner
to put it in the food box,

32:08.440 --> 32:09.920
and the butler has already taken it.

32:09.920 --> 32:11.270
Let's wait here for a while.

32:11.270 --> 32:12.360
Let's see if he's willing to come out

32:12.360 --> 32:14.080
and meet us after he reads it.

32:14.160 --> 32:15.510
Why did you use my name?

32:16.410 --> 32:17.170
Be quiet.

32:38.640 --> 32:39.790
Don't look for me.

32:40.240 --> 32:41.840
The wontons have gone mushy.

32:42.200 --> 32:43.680
Your method didn't work.

32:48.940 --> 32:50.070
Something's wrong.

32:50.330 --> 32:51.500
This is Xing's handwriting.

32:51.500 --> 32:52.500
Stop looking.

32:52.830 --> 32:54.640
Director Zhang is no longer here.

32:54.640 --> 32:56.830
The Ministry of Works decided to build
a river channel yesterday.

32:56.830 --> 32:59.070
He has moved to
the Manufacturing Bureau overnight.

32:59.070 --> 33:00.330
If you want to find him,

33:00.400 --> 33:01.350
I can help you.

33:01.880 --> 33:04.340
But we want
an additional 10 percent profit.

33:07.850 --> 33:08.770
This is risky.

33:08.800 --> 33:09.930
I'm not helping you.

33:10.860 --> 33:11.900
I'm helping Li Ce.

33:13.400 --> 33:13.990
Besides,

33:14.920 --> 33:17.320
I have the map
of the Manufacturing Bureau.

33:25.440 --> 33:26.030
Qiao,

33:26.720 --> 33:28.780
this is the outfit I specially bought

33:29.890 --> 33:31.350
for tonight's operation.

33:31.440 --> 33:33.960
Am I breathtakingly handsome

33:34.160 --> 33:36.070
and unrivaled in the world?

33:36.550 --> 33:38.480
Something like breaking into
the Manufacturing Bureau at night—

33:38.480 --> 33:40.340
Zhuge Yue can handle it on his own.

33:40.550 --> 33:42.150
You don't know martial arts.

33:42.530 --> 33:43.290
If you go...

33:43.310 --> 33:43.940
Qiao,

33:44.350 --> 33:45.400
don't worry.

33:45.960 --> 33:47.590
It's inconvenient
for Zhuge Yue to show up.

33:47.590 --> 33:49.410
I must use my identity as the Crown Prince

33:49.410 --> 33:51.410
to persuade Director Zhang to help.

33:52.000 --> 33:52.800
Rest assured.

33:53.110 --> 33:54.480
I've memorized the map
of the Manufacturing Bureau

33:54.480 --> 33:55.680
drawn by Wang Shi'er.

33:55.880 --> 33:58.160
Zhuge Yue will be fine with me.

33:58.510 --> 33:59.240
Li Ce,

34:00.030 --> 34:02.350
actually, you don't have to cooperate
with Zhuge Yue.

34:02.350 --> 34:03.610
According to our plan,

34:03.720 --> 34:05.320
we can build up our own power.

34:05.680 --> 34:07.660
We don't need his 30 percent share
of the gold mine

34:07.660 --> 34:10.120
to expand our power
and counter the Empress.

34:13.840 --> 34:14.480
Qiao.

34:16.070 --> 34:18.440
I said I'd take you back to Biantang
to recover,

34:18.440 --> 34:20.170
but since you came back with me,

34:20.880 --> 34:23.010
you've been living in constant danger

34:23.340 --> 34:25.070
without a single peaceful day.

34:26.199 --> 34:28.330
I've played the fool for so many years.

34:29.110 --> 34:31.370
I said I wanted to regroup and start over,

34:32.230 --> 34:33.070
but in the end,

34:34.840 --> 34:37.699
I still have to rely on you
to fight my battles for me.

34:37.920 --> 34:40.670
I feel very bad about it.

34:46.150 --> 34:46.710
However,

34:47.070 --> 34:47.880
I have always been a good man

34:47.880 --> 34:49.610
who repays evil with kindness.

34:50.630 --> 34:52.750
So you've always had someone else
in your heart

34:52.750 --> 34:54.270
and treated me roughly,

34:55.030 --> 34:56.290
but it doesn't matter.

34:56.580 --> 34:58.510
I've already left a way out for you.

34:58.520 --> 35:00.080
Inside here are over 50

35:00.100 --> 35:02.360
shop deeds from various cities
across Biantang and Great Yong,

35:02.360 --> 35:03.910
along with thousands of mu
of fertile farmland.

35:03.910 --> 35:05.910
If anything happens to me this time,

35:06.270 --> 35:07.710
go to the pawnshop, get the money,

35:07.710 --> 35:08.840
and leave Biantang.

35:18.460 --> 35:20.260
You're getting physical again!

35:21.230 --> 35:22.140
Jinx.

35:39.080 --> 35:40.030
Strange.

35:44.340 --> 35:46.700
Where is that

35:48.220 --> 35:49.480
"Water Conservancy"?

36:00.670 --> 36:02.030
Who are you?

36:04.430 --> 36:05.290
Your Highness.

36:08.150 --> 36:10.210
It's not your first day working here.

36:10.440 --> 36:12.680
Don't you know the Crown Prince wants
Honghe fish?

36:12.680 --> 36:14.070
Of course I know.

36:14.840 --> 36:17.000
But Honghe fish is rare

36:17.400 --> 36:19.200
and only sold in the West Market.

36:19.360 --> 36:21.840
I usually go early in the morning

36:21.910 --> 36:23.670
to get the fresh ones.

36:23.920 --> 36:27.150
But unfortunately,
I was a quarter of an hour late today.

36:27.880 --> 36:29.440
The best Honghe fish

36:29.700 --> 36:31.380
was sent to the Zhan's Manor.

36:32.010 --> 36:32.950
Honghe fish?

36:33.460 --> 36:34.060
Sister,

36:34.210 --> 36:35.370
this is Honghe fish.

36:35.480 --> 36:36.400
It's very rare.

36:41.450 --> 36:42.100
Your Highness.

36:42.100 --> 36:42.960
Your Highness.

36:43.190 --> 36:44.030
Are you saying

36:44.160 --> 36:46.020
Lord Zhan also likes Honghe fish?

36:46.710 --> 36:47.840
Yes, Your Highness.

36:48.720 --> 36:51.850
It's said that, apart from me,
the only regular customer

36:51.930 --> 36:53.880
of the shop selling Honghe fish
in the West Market

36:53.880 --> 36:55.550
is Zhan's Mansion.

37:12.430 --> 37:13.070
Princess Fu.

37:13.070 --> 37:14.070
Where is your lady?

37:14.070 --> 37:14.710
Our lady?

37:17.630 --> 37:18.920
She was sleeping here

37:18.920 --> 37:19.960
just an hour ago.

37:20.930 --> 37:22.290
Where did she go?

37:27.740 --> 37:28.340
Take care.

37:31.280 --> 37:31.960
Ziming...

37:32.800 --> 37:34.060
works for the Empress!

37:35.180 --> 37:38.070
[One day ago]

38:19.630 --> 38:20.430
Catch them!

38:22.670 --> 38:24.480
Your Majesty, are you feeling guilty

38:24.480 --> 38:25.750
that you don't dare to see me?

38:25.750 --> 38:27.090
If you can't get rid of him,

38:27.090 --> 38:28.520
you are nothing but useless trash.

38:28.520 --> 38:30.050
Get out! Get out, all of you!

38:30.060 --> 38:32.690
If you like me, marry me
and make me your princess consort.

38:32.690 --> 38:36.290
And bring a moment of peace
to the millions of people in Great Yan!

38:36.370 --> 38:37.570
There are some things

38:37.980 --> 38:39.100
I must do.
